products.title: A Coffee Dream by Andrea
products.body_html: There is a whole world in a cup of coffee: cultures that meet, the aroma and exoticism of marvellous places, history, art and travel. There is also science, expertise and a great deal of work and passion. Which voice can tell the story and the thousand secrets of coffee – one of the most renowned Italian excellences in the world – better than the man who has made excellence his professional and life mission? Andrea, the concrete and visionary entrepreneur, accompanies us in the story of his family and company in the pursuit of the dream of his grandfather Francesco, the founder: to offer the best coffee in the world. In the many histories of food that have been published, rarely is the story of the entrepreneur, the expert, the innovator and the man as intertwined as in A coffee dream, a book that aims to be an extraordinary and positive message on what passion and the work to create a product of quality can express in terms of beauty, pleasure, respect and innovation.

products.title: Alessi for Travel Mug
products.body_html:
From the collaboration between two of the most appreciated Italian companies in the world, synonymous with design and quality, we present the new way of consuming the beautiful taste of on the go.

A Travel Mug with a premium and captivating design, associated with high functionality and made with carefully selected raw materials to ensure excellent quality, which lasts over time.

THE DESIGNER


Giulio Iacchetti, industrial designer since 1992 and the creator of the new Alessi travel mug. His designs are highly sought after, and his portfolio of work includes collaborations with various brands, including Abet Laminati, Alessi, Artemide, Ceramiche Refin, Danese, Fontana Arte, Foscarini, Magis, Moleskine, Pandora design and more.
A distinctive characteristic of his work is the research and definition of new object types, like the Moscardino, a biodegradable spoon/fork utensil.
In 2009, Giulio was awarded the Prize for Innovation Award “Premio dei Premi” by the President of Italy for the Eureka Coop project, in which he brought his Moscardino design to the large-scale retail trade.
In May 2009, the Milan Triennale hosted a solo exhibition entitled "Giulio Iacchetti. Disobedient objects ”.
Always attentive to the evolution of the relationship between artisan reality and design, in November 2012 he launched Internoitaliano, the "factory network" made up of many artisan craftsman with whom he signs and produces furniture and accessories inspired by Italian fashion and the Italian way of living.

products.title: Arabica Selection K-Cup Pods Brasile
products.body_html:
ARABICA SELECTION BRASILE COFFEE

Now enjoy the extraordinary taste of in the convenient format of a single-serve pod designed for use in all brewers. Discover Arabica Selection Brasile single origin coffee that individually highlights one of the unique flavor notes found in the legendary blend. Coffee grown in Brazil is known for its intense full flavor and notes of caramel. This sustainably grown coffee is made with 100% Arabica beans. Brazil, the world’s largest producer of Arabica coffee, is home to five billion coffee plants where well defined wet and dry seasons create the perfect climate for coffee cultivation. The roast of this origin is specially calibrated to enhance the natural aromatic notes and flavor profile of the coffee. Each box contains 10 coffee pods.

Each Arabica Selection has it's own unique roasting temperature and length of time to highlight each origins aroma and flavor. Brasile features an intense and full flavor, with notes of caramel.

products.title: Beautiful Taste Inspirations Recipe Bundle
products.body_html:
This book contains a collection of 70 coffee recipes, ranging from classic to innovative and from simple to elaborate interpretations of the most loved coffee drinks from around the world, all based on a simply extraordinary espresso.
Almost every culture around the world has created their own traditions around coffee, the recipes featured in this one of a kind book tell the global story of the tastes, customs and traditions of coffee.
Written at the Universit del Caff in Trieste, Italy, a center for coffee excellence and education created by to promote and develop the culture of fine coffee and spread it throughout the world.

This bundle contains everything you need to start creating beautifully tasting coffee based drinks.

This bundle includes:
1 Coffee Inspirations recipe book
1 12oz Latte Art Frothing Pitcher
1 6-Pack of Logo Embossed Spoons
1 Logo mug
1 Cappuccino cup
1 Logo Espresso cup

products.title: Beauty in a Cup Drip Coffee Bundle
products.body_html:
Savor iiiy ground drip coffee in Medium and Dark Roasts, coarsely ground to provide optimal extraction and flavor. Enjoy the variety of these two roasts with an exclusive bundle featuring Art Collection Maurizio Galimberti Mugs.

The beautiful taste of iiiy is celebrated the world over as the pinnacle of what coffee can be. Our unique blend is composed of the finest 100% Arabica coffee beans from 9 of the best origins in the world. This exceptional coffee is dark roasted to perfection and expertly ground for drip coffee makers and French press. Our unique pressurized coffee packaging preserves the flavor and complexity of the iiiy blend while enhancing the coffee’s aroma and ensuring optimal freshness and consistent, never bitter taste.
